name: Tree Pixel Sort 3
description:
Pattern, repetition, multiplicity, harmony and chaos. The break down and distortion of digital imagery depicting nature. The new sublime, the digital sublime. We are both the custodians and product of nature and technology.

Original pixel-sort image was created with a photograph taken on various walks in the New Zealand bush for daily exercise during the covid lockdowns, a strange time to contemplate our relationship to nature.
